By: Akpan Sunday Veteran Nollywood actor, Emeka Ike, has welcomed a baby girl with his second wife, Yolanda Pfeiffer. The excited actor took to his Instagram page on Tuesday to share the good news. The proud father shared the photo of the bouncing baby while appreciating his wife. The newly born, who he named Oluchi, was delivered in Nuremberg, Germany. He described the baby as his “bundle of joy”. “GUESS WHO IS IN TOWN?… Oluchi…in Nuremberg Germany … Thank u for the bundle of Joy… ” he tweeted.